# Pin YAML to LF across Windows edits + WSL/mini (Order NW-1).
# An editor flipped ai_capex_cycle.yaml LF->CRLF mid-order, producing
# whole-file line-ending churn in the diff. eol=lf makes git normalize
# YAML to LF in the repo regardless of how the working file was written,
# so theme-config diffs show only real content changes.
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
